archimate:ArchimateDiagramModel.documentation:
This view introduces the key threats and vulnerabilities for the audit deviations.
If the threats would occur, there is high possibility that Tietoevry Tech Services will face following events:
- Loss of reputation, as we are assuring our compliance in public and in customer contracts - Possible sanctions and penalties due violation of GDPR regulations or customer contracts - Loss of confidentiality, integrity and availability of the data due data breach
Each threat and vulnerability is described within the element documentation below
